               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t16910527-14-defend40" type="defendantName">
                  Margaret 
                  Beard
               <interp inst="t16910527-14-defend40" type="surname" value="Beard"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-defend40" type="given" value="Margaret"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-defend40" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-defend40" type="age" value="12"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , a <rs id="t16910527-14-deflabel62" type="occupation">Girle</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910527-14-defend40 t16910527-14-deflabel62"></join>, about 12 Years of Age, was Indicted for <rs id="t16910527-14-off63" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-off63" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-off63" type="offenceSubcategory" value="shoplifting"></interp>
               stealing a piece of Silk, value 6 l. from 
                     <persName id="t16910527-14-victim41" type="victimName">
                        <rs id="t16910527-14-viclabel64" type="occupation">Mr.</rs>
                        <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910527-14-victim41 t16910527-14-viclabel64"></join> 
                        Coldicot
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-victim41" type="surname" value="Coldicot"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t16910527-14-victim41" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <join result="offenceVictim" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910527-14-off63 t16910527-14-victim41"></join>
                     </persName>
                  , near Ludgate. She came to the Prosecutors Shop to buy some Silk, and stole away the piece afore said
            </rs>; and when she was pursued, she dropt it out of her Pettycoat. She was very impudent in her Behaviour when taken, and had been an Old Offender, though Young; she said that she was drawn away by wicked Company: In the end she was Found <rs id="t16910527-14-verdict65" type="verdictDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-verdict65" type="verdictCategory" value="guilty"></interp>
               Guilty
            </rs>, &amp;c.</p>
               <p>
                  <rs id="t16910527-14-punish66" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-punish66" type="punishmentCategory" value="death"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t16910527-14-punish66" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="respited"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t16910527-14-defend40 t16910527-14-punish66"></join>
               
                     <note>[Death -respited. See summary.]</note>
               
                  </rs>
               </p>
